                    <div class="feat-two-text">
                        <p><strong>Recyclable garbage</strong> includes waste paper, plastics, glass, metals and textiles.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
		</div>
         <div class="row">
            <div class="col-xs-12 col-lg-10 col-lg-offset-1" style="border-bottom:solid 1px #ddd;">
